{"type":"message","id":"04cfa05e","parentId":"410919fd","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:30:28.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"yaal here?\" which seems like a casual greeting or check-in. \"Yaal\" might be a typo or slang for \"y'all\" (are you all here?). \n\nGiven the context that I'm Samael, one of the Council agents, and Lucy just did a few one-word OK checks (which felt like testing connectivity), I should respond briefly and confirm presence.\n\nThis is a straightforward greeting/check-in, so I should respond naturally as Samael would.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Yes — I'm here. Council is operational. 🔍\n\nWhat do you need?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":144,"cacheRead":18662,"cacheWrite":27,"totalTokens":18843,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00072,"cacheRead":0.0018662000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.00003375,"total":0.0026299500000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772994625948}}
