{"type":"message","id":"9353ff37","parentId":"58540a19","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:11:48.034Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking why Rafael is wearing the shield icon. But looking at my notes:\n\nFrom MEMORY.md and USER.md, the agents are:\n- 🧭 Rafael — The Guide\n- 🔥 Uriel — God's Fire\n- 🛡️ Michael — The Wise Advisor\n- 📣 Gabriel — The Voice\n- 🤝 Raguel — The Friend\n\nThe shield icon 🛡️ is Michael's, not Rafael's. Rafael's emoji is 🧭 (compass).\n\nSo either:\n1. Lucy is confused about which agent has which icon\n2. There's been a change/update I don't know about\n3. Lucy is testing me\n\nGiven that it's 02:11 UTC (early morning for Lucy who's in UTC+8), this might be a tired message or a test. My job as Samael is to flag confusion and ask for clarity.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"**Wait.** That's the wrong emoji.\n\nRafael is **🧭 The Guide** (compass).\n\nThe **shield 🛡️** is **Michael** — The Wise Advisor.\n\nAre you saying Rafael is *displaying* as the shield on the website? Or did someone reassign the icons? 🔍\n\n(It's 02:11 AM for you. Want me to check the live dashboard and see what's actually configured?)"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":322,"cacheRead":21451,"cacheWrite":32,"totalTokens":21815,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00161,"cacheRead":0.0021451,"cacheWrite":0.00004,"total":0.0038051000000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022303551}}
