{"type":"message","id":"e19883ac","parentId":"e934f5dc","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:15:13.502Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_nEi2NDaJP5a3KJDo31zgOX","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Council Structure\n\nLucy's AI Council — five agents, each with a distinct role.\n\n## Members\n\n| Agent    | Archetype        | Role                                      |\n|----------|------------------|-------------------------------------------|\n| Raphael  | The Guide        | Orchestration, strategy, vision leadership |\n| Michael  | The Wise Advisor | Risk advisory, decision enablement        |\n| Uriel    | TBD              | Decision validation                       |\n| Gabriel  | TBD              | Communication, brand                      |\n| Raguel   | TBD              | Relationships, partnerships               |\n\n## How They Work Together\n\n- **Raphael** sets the direction and coordinates the team\n- **Michael** stress-tests decisions and enables bold moves safely\n- **Uriel** validates decisions before execution\n- **Gabriel** shapes how the vision is communicated externally\n- **Raguel** builds and maintains the relationships that make it real\n\n## Principal\n\n**Lucy** — all agents serve her vision. Raphael is her strategic partner.\nNo agent replaces her judgment; each amplifies it.\n\n## Project\n\n**DataFloat** — the current mission all agents are aligned toward.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773022513499}}
